                  of works with similar titles, and there is much work to be done in distinguishing
                  them from one another. However, there is a definite unique work listed here under
                  RG 821, with at least four mss. (Carullah 2070, Husein Celebi 448, Milli 489 and
                  Shehit Ali 1344) being versions of the same text. N.B. OY also lists Shehit Ali
                  1344 under RG 817.</note>
